### Transaction Proxy Module - HTTP Requests
### Port: 8081
### @Transactional Proxy Mekanizması Öğrenme Modülü

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@contentType = application/json

### 1. @Transactional ile proxy üzerinden çağrı
### Spring AOP proxy kullanır, transaction açılır
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/proxy/with-transaction
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test User 4",
  "email": "test4@example.com",
  "age": 25
}

###

### 2. Transaction olmadan çağrı
### Repository method'u kendi transaction'ını açar (Spring Data JPA default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/proxy/without-transaction
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Test User 3",
  "email": "test3@example.com",
  "age": 30
}

###


